cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea5' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the uplink carrier bandwidth to an out-of-range value of 200 will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper cell setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將上行載波頻寬設定為超出範圍的值 200，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的細胞設置。
